data.description: Welcome to your serene sanctuary nestled within a gated community with open space views of lush greenery. Oak Crest Village, an all age gated community, featuring trails, 2 pools, clubhouse, sports court, exterior maintenance and more.    This charming single-story home, just over 1300 sq.ft. offers the  perfect blend of comfort and convenience.  Move-in ready w/vaulted ceilings, living room with cozy fireplace and recently updated laminated flooring throughout. Fresh interior paint, newer appliances and HVAC. Unwind on your private balcony and be surrounded by the beauty of nature.  Take advantage of the nearby walking trails, perfect for morning strolls. The home is situated at the back of the community, conveniently located near guest parking and the greenbelt. Enjoy the access to exclusive amenities, HOA includes exterior maintenance, roof, two community pools, tennis courts and a clubhouse where you can participate in a variety of engaging activities. The allure of outdoor living awaits just beyond your doorstep!
